{"tid":1491405,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[抵制]其實如果政府啲記招無記者喺度會點架呢？","createTime":"2019-08-20T11:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T12:06:18.000Z","uid":131125,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"02ad8807d56af88f9ad893c327e198e2679d5e9f","tid":1491405,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:56:41.000Z","msg":"今日個大媽記大頭好明顯係要秋後算帳啦<br />\n尋日都斬得記者，分分鐘都係有計劃有預謀<br />\n傳媒除左發聲明譴責之外真係無野做到？<br />\n真係就咁由前線記者繼續俾人斬俾狗咬？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">首先要狗方發聲明交代果個大媽到底做咩會影大頭同埋會唔會恰當處理<br />\n如果唔係無限期杯葛政府同狗方發起嘅所有記招</span></span><br />\n<br />\n面對政府同狗嘅無恥升級<br />\n傳媒都應該對得起自己嘅專業而升級<br />\n我知實有紅底傳媒你地connect唔到<br />\n但紅底傳媒前線都係人黎架<br />\n都會驚會有生命危險架<br />\n公司唔肯抵制就唯有自己出手<br />\n<br />\n我知好多記者都好專業甚至唔怕自身安危<br />\n但呢種損害新聞自由嘅環境就係因為專業所以先必須做啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b13ef3c376b4d8193c8a7a4215f1ac9bbb3a732","tid":1491405,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:57:34.000Z","msg":"已經三權俾侵蝕得七七八八<br />\n唔想第四權嘅環境都一直俾人染黑落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc78b660def7dba020a1678c4f556537958d5e8","tid":1491405,"uid":195120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:58:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a3c8fa8eb84fcb392298b9cf3b447517cf7227c","tid":1491405,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:58:21.000Z","msg":"另外集思廣益下除左記者佢地<br />\n我地作為普通市民有啲咩可以做去維護傳媒同新聞自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f867d109b7eacc6a3f08da99cc438df0dd79e6f3","tid":1491405,"uid":60872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:58:58.000Z","msg":"首先連登仔唔好一有政府記者會就即刻驚跟唔貼政府風向 不斷推post先"},{"pid":"c34d504de4c3698cad4644e37547beffc87851d8","tid":1491405,"uid":54264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:59:20.000Z","msg":"一定有TVB你放心"},{"pid":"69cb626548cb0f8fd0d89fb7c03b1829a119ddd9","tid":1491405,"uid":213747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:59:39.000Z","msg":"會得返cctvb同大公新華記者同黑警格劍"},{"pid":"001cbcdddaf9ea3587fdc11fabce84bc95336730","tid":1491405,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:59:55.000Z","msg":"大家回想下咁多畫面咁多照咁多片<br />\n都係前線記者一手一腳影出黎<br />\n先可以打動到外國同埋香港大多數嘅關心<br />\n佢地而家開始俾人打擊數人頭啦<br />\n我地唔係唔理唔做野唔嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d87a327aa2a604e113a384a990a148d5fb35f8","tid":1491405,"uid":122676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:00:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"200a28aa5a8b5aef10cb1824f00d292fc8cc4f1b","tid":1491405,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:01:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1490061/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1490061/page/1</a><br />\n前線既一封信 前線表示唔可以袋住先, 幫手正評推上熱門"},{"pid":"8bdbfa3c26e452a198999471c84529442eff400e","tid":1491405,"uid":47311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:01:56.000Z","msg":"咁咪全場 Chinazi 『記者』囉on9"},{"pid":"2398f032a6510d4ed6124061c66c32ee59c2a62f","tid":1491405,"uid":45893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:03:05.000Z","msg":"變成CCTVB獨家直播"},{"pid":"542393c3db567a510c71044ac5130132a889dc61","tid":1491405,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13d87a327aa2a604e113a384a990a148d5fb35f8","tid":1491405,"uid":122676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:00:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:03:10.000Z","msg":"前線即席缺席行唔行得通<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然已經同罷工無咩分別<br />\n<br />\n仲有得返cctvb同大公最少啲記招無咁多人關注先<br />\n不過同時我地就要準備啲野去滿足返觀眾眼睛，令佢地唔多想再睇政府/狗記招<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7002fe66ade9d2cfa9a1ae3d903aca9dab14a298","tid":1491405,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:06:18.000Z","msg":"不過都係當我無講過啦<br />\n連喺連登狗記招都可以keep住推唔停<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要外界對狗記招稍微抵制下似乎都係無咩可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}